**Description of the problem including expected versus actual behavior**: When running an EQL sequence query, the results are inconsistent with the `join_keys` being switched between records: the first sequence result has a `join_keys` set to `user1@domain1.com` and contains documents with `user.email` set to `user2@domain2.com`, the second sequence result has a `join_keys` set to `user2@domain2.com` and contains documents with `user.email` set to `user1@domain1.com`.

